sentences: Ola “the Swede” Englund (born 27 September 1981) is a Swedish musician, songwriter, record producer, guitarist, businessman, YouTuber and owner of Solar guitars.
In 2018 & 2019, Total Guitar magazine awarded him as Best Internet Personality.
In 2018 & 2019, Total Guitar magazine awarded him as Best Internet Personality.
On 24 March 2019, he released his first solo album Master Of The Universe.
His second solo album Starzinger was released on 26 April, 2021.
Englund has had signature guitar lines from Strictly 7 (2011-2013) and Washburn (2013-2017), as well as a signature amplifier from Randall (2014–2019).
